    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">THE STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">10 years ago, Vittoria's father was murdered by a worker in their orchard. It's now 1925, and the man makes a sudden reappearance in her life as the owner of a popular carnival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">When she meets a wayward circus performer who also has a bone to pick with the Don, the two scheme to teach him a lesson, at a deadly price.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Exploration-rich maps inspired by real locations in Sicily</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Dozens of hand-drawn illustrations and cutscenes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Experience the game by day and night over one week</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">A knife-wielding clown, a haunting, and an atmospheric carnival</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242730/extras/fe7e9b47e70f1296a5019899e045c56a.poster.avif?t=1769910970\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242730/extras/fe7e9b47e70f1296a5019899e045c56a.webm?t=1769910970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Inspired by the <i>verismo</i> (realism) operas of the early 1900s.</p>",
